data.revised_prompt: Create an image showcasing the vibrant Seattle skyline, with the iconic Space Needle dominating the scene. Employ the post-Impressionist style typically seen in Van Gogh's artwork, illustrating the cityscape with a swirl of luminous colors and an emphasis on emotional impact. Render it as if it's a painting crafted with dense strokes, comparable to the effect achieved using oil on canvas.
